    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事·序章</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在遥远的过去，世界曾被圣铠的力量拯救。彼时，大魔术士露奈狄亚创造出了魔法的铠甲，粉碎了阿比斯洛亚帝国统治整片大陆的企图。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自此，两百年已逝。如今，在大陆上实力最强，同时也弥漫着不祥气息的索尔炽纳特王国面前，继承露奈狄亚意志的国度——弥斯缇艾因的女王召集了诸国元首，谴责王国的作为……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211430/extras/1315af97e4e75d771e948e6f03af9d14.avif?t=1771034419\" width=780 height=438 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏模式介绍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>剧情模式</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验6个国度各自在“新生阿比斯洛亚帝国”夺权后发生的故事</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211430/extras/bc711c0c114eb44f92ef43ff18391f41.avif?t=1771034419\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>任务模式</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择24个国家中的一个来挑战其专属任务</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211430/extras/7668ab072db479a39f7304461911713a.avif?t=1771034419\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在有限时间内增强国力</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在编队阶段，玩家需要为接下来的战斗强化所选国家的战力。合理利用有限时间，是最大限度强化我军的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211430/extras/eada529785c852bcae9637d181a0bf9d.avif?t=1771034419\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >侵袭邻国，进一步壮大国家</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在攻击阶段，玩家可发兵侵袭他国，夺得当地的物资或强化麾下的兵员。是否侵袭对手，全凭玩家的个人意愿。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211430/extras/81d41c5dded82bcbd6b65e04c72fbbc7.avif?t=1771034419\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >有策略地指挥部队，歼灭敌对势力</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战役将在六角形棋盘上以回合制的方式展开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可自行决定战术：集中攻击敌方领袖，逼迫其撤退；或与敌方兵员交锋，逐一击破。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211430/extras/407d11e886964f6d3b2af13b8fba7cd6.avif?t=1771034419\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p>",
